# Housekeeping All Done Verification

## Overview

| Field | Value |
| ------- | ------- |
| Date | 2026-03-07 |
| Objective | Implement GitHub issue #3377 — clean up `issue-2722` worktree/branch after PR #3372 merged |
| Outcome | All cleanup already complete; created verification comment + empty commit + PR to close issue |
| Root Cause | Housekeeping was done out-of-band; issue just needed formal closure |

## When to Use

Use when an issue describes **pure housekeeping** with no code deliverables:
- Delete a git branch or remove a worktree
- Close another GitHub issue
- Verify a PR was merged and artifacts cleaned up

## Verified Workflow

```bash
# Confirm PR merged
gh pr view <PR-number> --json state,mergedAt,mergeCommit

# Check artifacts
git worktree list | grep <issue-name>
git branch -a | grep <branch-name>
git ls-remote --heads origin <branch-name>
gh issue view <issue-number> --json state

# Cleanup remaining artifacts
git worktree remove .worktrees/<name> && git worktree prune
git push origin --delete <branch-name>
gh issue close <number> --comment "..."

# Post verification comment
gh issue comment <issue-number> --body "## Cleanup Verification ..."

# Empty commit + PR
git commit --allow-empty -m "chore(cleanup): verify <description>
Refs #<issue-number>"
git push -u origin <branch-name>
gh pr create --title "chore(cleanup): ..." --body "..."
```

## Failed Attempts

| Attempt | What Was Tried | Why It Failed | Lesson Learned |
| --------- | ---------------- | --------------- | ---------------- |
| Searching for code to change | Looked for source files to modify | No code changes needed | Read issue category first; "clean up worktree/branch" = no code |
| Delete branch locally first | `git branch -d issue-2722` | Branch didn't exist locally — already gone | Check `git branch -a` AND `git ls-remote` for both local + remote |

## Verified On

| Project | Context | Details |
| --------- | --------- | --------- |
| ProjectOdyssey | Issue #3377, branch `3377-auto-impl`, PR #4044 | Verifying cleanup of `issue-2722` worktree/branch after PR #3372 merged |

